        "content": "## Worker & queue metrics\n\nThese panels target **`django-prometheus`** on the API (`job=django-api`). To chart workers, expose `/metrics` from the worker Deployment and add a scrape job (for example `django-worker`). For **Amazon SQS queue depth**, use the AWS CloudWatch data source or `yet-another-cloudwatch-exporter` — not included in this MVP manifest set."
